name: defcoordinators
sql:
CREATE TABLE `defcoordinators` (
`dcid` INTEGER NOT NULL ,
`firstname` TEXT DEFAULT NULL,
`lastname` TEXT DEFAULT NULL,
`rating` INTEGER DEFAULT NULL,
`salary` INTEGER DEFAULT NULL, scheme INTEGER,
PRIMARY KEY (`dcid`)
)

name: players
sql:
CREATE TABLE `players` (
`pid` INTEGER NOT NULL ,
`firstname` TEXT NOT NULL,
`lastname` TEXT NOT NULL,
`tid` INTEGER NOT NULL,
`birthyear` INTEGER NOT NULL,
`position` TEXT NOT NULL,
`jersey` INTEGER NOT NULL,
`state` TEXT NOT NULL,
`rating` INTEGER DEFAULT NULL,
PRIMARY KEY (`pid`),
FOREIGN KEY (`tid`) REFERENCES `teams` (`tid`)
)

name: teams
sql:
CREATE TABLE `teams` (
`tid` INTEGER NOT NULL ,
`cid` INTEGER NOT NULL,
`did` INTEGER NOT NULL,
`school` TEXT NOT NULL,
`state` TEXT NOT NULL,
`prestige` INTEGER NOT NULL,
`budget` INTEGER DEFAULT NULL,
`ocid` INTEGER DEFAULT NULL,
`dcid` INTEGER DEFAULT NULL,
`ranking` tinyINTEGER DEFAULT NULL,
`wins` INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
`losses` INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0, "oppwins" INTEGER NULL,
PRIMARY KEY (`tid`),
FOREIGN KEY (`dcid`) REFERENCES `defcoordinators` (`dcid`),
FOREIGN KEY (`ocid`) REFERENCES `offcoordinators` (`ocid`)
)

name: offcoordinators
sql:
CREATE TABLE "offcoordinators" (
    ocid INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
    firstname TEXT,
    lastname TEXT,
    rating INTEGER,
    salary INTEGER
, scheme INTEGER)

name: player_stats
sql:
CREATE TABLE `player_stats` (
  `sid` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `pid` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `completions` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attempts` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `yards` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `receptions` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `targets` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tackles` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sacks` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  CONSTRAINT `fk_pid` FOREIGN KEY (`pid`) REFERENCES `players` (`pid`)
)

name: scores
sql:
CREATE TABLE scores (
    normal TEXT,
    close TEXT,
    blowout TEXT
)

name: states
sql:
CREATE TABLE `states` (
  `sid` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `abbrev` varchar(2) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`sid`)
)

name: achievements
